/* III conformance corpus 189 -- Stage 3.15: em-dash in block comment.
 * The iiis-0 lexer once terminated a block comment early at U+2014
 * (em-dash), lexing the rest as code.  Fixed: this comment contains an
 * em-dash — and continues with words after it that must stay inside
 * the comment.  If the U+2014 still terminated the comment, "and
 * continues..." would lex as code and the file would not compile.
 * Exit = 99. */
module corpus_189
fn main() -> u64 { return 99u64 }
